marketing: Shell Gadus S2 V20XKD Grease is a premium quality, non-lead multi-purpose product based on lithium soap. It was originally conceived and patented by Shell and has continuously been improved over the years. Its multi-purpose nature allows for use in both heavy duty automotive and industrial applications, thus reducing the need for specialty greases in specific applications. Shell Gadus S2 V20XKD Grease is offered in NLGI grade 0 and contains 1% moly.
